How I Recreated It: https://youtu.be/2gz6FEIm7Io

same location. same outfit kinda sorta. different guy. 20 years later🐘 @jawed

Travelled from Australia to San Diego Zoo with my awesome brother and mum to recreate this iconic video, was such a cool experience. thank yall for the support!! HAPPY BIRTHDAY YOUTUBE!
